"{\"uid\": \"metro.co.uk-2024-07-18-brits-heading-olympics-paris-need-know-this-driving-law-21255740\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"Brits heading to theOlympicsthis year via car could end up with a hefty fine and points on their licence if they do not know this law in France.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 144, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 137, \"end\": 143, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.8030524171435611, \"rank\": 0.24168333706893583, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Brits\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 5}, {\"ngram\": \"theOlympicsthis year\", \"from\": 17, \"to\": 37}, {\"ngram\": \"car\", \"from\": 42, \"to\": 45}, {\"ngram\": \"a hefty fine\", \"from\": 64, \"to\": 76}, {\"ngram\": \"their licence\", \"from\": 91, \"to\": 104}, {\"ngram\": \"this law\", \"from\": 125, \"to\": 133}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As thesummerholidays approach and with theParisOlympics on the horizon, British motorists planning to drive in France are being urged to familiarise themselves with localdrivinglaws.\", \"from\": 146, \"to\": 328, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 218, \"end\": 225, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9999843931977072, \"rank\": 1.3143442434930753e-05, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}, {\"begin\": 257, \"end\": 263, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.8030524171435611, \"rank\": 0.24168333706893583, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"thesummerholidays\", \"from\": 149, \"to\": 166}, {\"ngram\": \"theParisOlympics\", \"from\": 185, \"to\": 201}, {\"ngram\": \"the horizon\", \"from\": 205, \"to\": 216}, {\"ngram\": \"localdrivinglaws\", \"from\": 311, \"to\": 327}]}, {\"sentence\": \"One of the key regulations that might catch British drivers off guard is the banning of wearing headphones or headsets while driving.\", \"from\": 330, \"to\": 463, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 374, \"end\": 381, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9999843931977072, \"rank\": 1.3143442434930753e-05, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the key regulations\", \"from\": 337, \"to\": 356}, {\"ngram\": \"guard\", \"from\": 394, \"to\": 399}, {\"ngram\": \"the banning\", \"from\": 403, \"to\": 414}, {\"ngram\": \"headphones\", \"from\": 426, \"to\": 436}, {\"ngram\": \"headsets\", \"from\": 440, \"to\": 448}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Graham Conway from Select Car Leasing said: 'While many French driving laws mirror those in the UK, some are less familiar to Brits, such as the ban on using ear pieces.'\", \"from\": 465, \"to\": 635, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 465, \"end\": 471, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Benjamin_Graham\", \"score\": 0.9999141380996462, \"rank\": 8.582726082765325e-05, \"text\": \"Graham\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q188094\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Benjamin_Graham\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Benjamin_Graham\"}, {\"begin\": 472, \"end\": 478, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Conwy\", \"score\": 0.6206920947194987, \"rank\": 0.611104778854919, \"text\": \"Conway\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Conwy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Conwy\"}, {\"begin\": 521, \"end\": 527, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9998452151804451, \"rank\": 8.807173042119832e-05, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}, {\"begin\": 561, \"end\": 563, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9999987295640379, \"rank\": 1.2646845018101274e-06, \"text\": \"UK\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Select Car Leasing\", \"from\": 484, \"to\": 502}, {\"ngram\": \"Brits\", \"from\": 591, \"to\": 596}, {\"ngram\": \"the ban\", \"from\": 606, \"to\": 613}, {\"ngram\": \"ear pieces\", \"from\": 623, \"to\": 633}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Modern cars come equipped with advanced sound systems and in-built microphones, making the use of headphones redundant.\", \"from\": 637, \"to\": 756, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Modern cars\", \"from\": 637, \"to\": 648}, {\"ngram\": \"advanced sound systems\", \"from\": 668, \"to\": 690}, {\"ngram\": \"in-built microphones\", \"from\": 695, \"to\": 715}, {\"ngram\": \"the use\", \"from\": 724, \"to\": 731}, {\"ngram\": \"headphones redundant\", \"from\": 735, \"to\": 755}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Start your day informed with Metro'sNews Updatesnewsletter or getBreaking Newsalerts the moment it happens.\", \"from\": 758, \"to\": 865, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"your day\", \"from\": 764, \"to\": 772}, {\"ngram\": \"Metro'sNews Updatesnewsletter\", \"from\": 787, \"to\": 816}, {\"ngram\": \"getBreaking Newsalerts\", \"from\": 820, \"to\": 842}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, drivers of older car models might still resort to headphones for phone calls or listening to podcasts.\", \"from\": 867, \"to\": 978, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"drivers\", \"from\": 876, \"to\": 883}, {\"ngram\": \"older car models\", \"from\": 887, \"to\": 903}, {\"ngram\": \"headphones\", \"from\": 926, \"to\": 936}, {\"ngram\": \"phone calls\", \"from\": 941, \"to\": 952}, {\"ngram\": \"podcasts\", \"from\": 969, \"to\": 977}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Mr Conway has warned against this practice, emphasising the safety risks involved.\", \"from\": 980, \"to\": 1062, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 983, \"end\": 989, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Conwy\", \"score\": 0.6206920947194987, \"rank\": 0.611104778854919, \"text\": \"Conway\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Conwy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Conwy\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this practice\", \"from\": 1009, \"to\": 1022}, {\"ngram\": \"the safety risks\", \"from\": 1036, \"to\": 1052}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He said: 'Not being able to hear your surroundings is incredibly dangerous.\", \"from\": 1064, \"to\": 1139, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"your surroundings\", \"from\": 1097, \"to\": 1114}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You could miss critical sounds like emergency sirens, honking horns, or even nearby cyclists and pedestrians.\", \"from\": 1140, \"to\": 1249, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"critical sounds\", \"from\": 1155, \"to\": 1170}, {\"ngram\": \"emergency sirens\", \"from\": 1176, \"to\": 1192}, {\"ngram\": \"honking horns\", \"from\": 1194, \"to\": 1207}, {\"ngram\": \"even nearby cyclists\", \"from\": 1212, \"to\": 1232}, {\"ngram\": \"pedestrians\", \"from\": 1237, \"to\": 1248}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'In France, this is not just unsafe but illegal.\", \"from\": 1251, \"to\": 1299, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1255, \"end\": 1261, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.8030524171435611, \"rank\": 0.24168333706893583, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Being caught can result in a fine of 135 euros (\\u00a3113) and three points on your licence.'\", \"from\": 1300, \"to\": 1388, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a fine\", \"from\": 1327, \"to\": 1333}, {\"ngram\": \"135 euros\", \"from\": 1337, \"to\": 1346}, {\"ngram\": \"three points\", \"from\": 1358, \"to\": 1370}, {\"ngram\": \"your licence\", \"from\": 1374, \"to\": 1386}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In addition to the headphone ban, there are other French road laws that British drivers might overlook, including the mandatory display of an emissions sticker, known as the Crit'Air vignette, on your vehicle.\", \"from\": 1390, \"to\": 1599, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1440, \"end\": 1446, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9998452151804451, \"rank\": 8.807173042119832e-05, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}, {\"begin\": 1462, \"end\": 1469, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9999843931977072, \"rank\": 1.3143442434930753e-05, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}, {\"begin\": 1564, \"end\": 1572, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Crit'air\", \"score\": 0.7523610626005415, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Crit'Air\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Crit'air\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Crit'air\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"addition\", \"from\": 1393, \"to\": 1401}, {\"ngram\": \"the headphone ban\", \"from\": 1405, \"to\": 1422}, {\"ngram\": \"the mandatory display\", \"from\": 1504, \"to\": 1525}, {\"ngram\": \"an emissions sticker\", \"from\": 1529, \"to\": 1549}, {\"ngram\": \"your vehicle\", \"from\": 1586, \"to\": 1598}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This sticker indicates the vehicle's emissions levels and is essential for driving in certain low-emission zones aimed at improving air quality.\", \"from\": 1601, \"to\": 1745, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"This sticker\", \"from\": 1601, \"to\": 1613}, {\"ngram\": \"the vehicle's emissions levels\", \"from\": 1624, \"to\": 1654}, {\"ngram\": \"certain low-emission zones\", \"from\": 1687, \"to\": 1713}, {\"ngram\": \"air quality\", \"from\": 1733, \"to\": 1744}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Failure to display this sticker can lead to a fine of up to 135 euros.\", \"from\": 1746, \"to\": 1816, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Failure\", \"from\": 1746, \"to\": 1753}, {\"ngram\": \"this sticker\", \"from\": 1765, \"to\": 1777}, {\"ngram\": \"a fine\", \"from\": 1790, \"to\": 1796}, {\"ngram\": \"up to 135 euros\", \"from\": 1800, \"to\": 1815}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Another significant regulation is the possession of speed camera detectors.\", \"from\": 1818, \"to\": 1893, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Another significant regulation\", \"from\": 1818, \"to\": 1848}, {\"ngram\": \"the possession\", \"from\": 1852, \"to\": 1866}, {\"ngram\": \"speed camera detectors\", \"from\": 1870, \"to\": 1892}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Mr Conway noted: 'Radar or laser detectors, which identify the presence of speed traps, are illegal in France regardless of whether they are in use.\", \"from\": 1895, \"to\": 2043, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1898, \"end\": 1904, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Conwy\", \"score\": 0.6206920947194987, \"rank\": 0.611104778854919, \"text\": \"Conway\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Conwy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Conwy\"}, {\"begin\": 1998, \"end\": 2004, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.8030524171435611, \"rank\": 0.24168333706893583, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Radar\", \"from\": 1913, \"to\": 1918}, {\"ngram\": \"laser detectors\", \"from\": 1922, \"to\": 1937}, {\"ngram\": \"the presence\", \"from\": 1954, \"to\": 1966}, {\"ngram\": \"speed traps\", \"from\": 1970, \"to\": 1981}, {\"ngram\": \"use\", \"from\": 2039, \"to\": 2042}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'If found with one, even if it's switched off, you could face a 1,500 euro fine, six points on your licence, and a three-year driving ban.\", \"from\": 2045, \"to\": 2183, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a 1,500 euro fine\", \"from\": 2107, \"to\": 2124}, {\"ngram\": \"your licence\", \"from\": 2140, \"to\": 2152}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'Understanding and adhering to local regulations can help ensure a safe and hassle-free trip, avoiding unexpected fines and penalties.\", \"from\": 2185, \"to\": 2319, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"local regulations\", \"from\": 2216, \"to\": 2233}, {\"ngram\": \"a safe and hassle-free trip\", \"from\": 2250, \"to\": 2277}, {\"ngram\": \"unexpected fines\", \"from\": 2288, \"to\": 2304}, {\"ngram\": \"penalties\", \"from\": 2309, \"to\": 2318}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'So if you are planning a trip to France - or any country for that matter - this summer, it is essential you take time to review the local laws.'\", \"from\": 2321, \"to\": 2466, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2355, \"end\": 2361, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.8030524171435611, \"rank\": 0.24168333706893583, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a trip\", \"from\": 2345, \"to\": 2351}, {\"ngram\": \"any country\", \"from\": 2367, \"to\": 2378}, {\"ngram\": \"that matter\", \"from\": 2383, \"to\": 2394}, {\"ngram\": \"time\", \"from\": 2435, \"to\": 2439}, {\"ngram\": \"the local laws\", \"from\": 2450, \"to\": 2464}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Get in touch with our news team by emailing 